 hus been made surround this with\nputty and fill the dam thus created\nwith turpentine to prevent heating. Do\nnot press too hard on the drill Ih bor\ning.\nIt U at such times that the man with a\npr\"|,. r k/. wUuisr of Ids car's construc\ntion I a? sit sdvaMSge ov?r the man\nwho merely knows how \\o drive.\nPrepare youri-lf tor occurrences like\nthe abo\\e t<v laV'in?\nSTK.tTTON-Bl.lSS\nAITUMOltILK t'Ol'RHK\nwherein you ;..n become thoroughly con\nvert an*. with the instruction, care ami\noj>' ration of your car.\nIt Inter now for SPRING COfRSR\nstarting March 1st. Two lessons a week\nfor four weeks.\nTuition Fee $10.00.\nf'taas A. Mon. and Wed., 4 to 0 P. M.\nClass is. Mon. and Wed.. 8 to 10 P M.\nCla*-* C, Tues. and Thurs., 8 to 10 P. M.\nStratton ISIiss Company,\nIMIDCK ISKOTMKRS DKAl.EitS\nInstruction l>t par In lent\n10'? Wet (iftli s\". Tel. CoitlOtbus 71(10.\nInvestigate\nIn the whole light six field you will not find\nthe quality of Velie construction combined\nwith such values as these at the Velie s low price:\n7-R Red Sea! Continental motor?the best motor\nContinental ever built?four bearing crankshaft?en\nduring bronze backed bearings everywhere?Timken\nAxles front and rear?Borg Beck Clutch Bijur\nStarting and Lighting.\nWith such features as these all through you have the\nroom, the style, and the Velie lasting mirror finish\nnot matched by any other.\nEight models: 5 and 7 passenger Touring, Sedans,\nRoadsters and Speedsters. Ask for a demonstration.\nGARLAND AUTOMOBILE CO.,\n1888 Broadway, at 62d St., N. Y.\nTel. Col. 5S96\nt-T\"\n\n9\nW3\nWM\nA\nTHIS IS THE\nOVERLAND CREED\nThat true service consists in\nfiner workmanship.\nThat a Rood mdtor car must be profit\nable for the people who buy it.\nThat the finest automobile advertise\nment on earth is a car that substantiates ia\npractice what it claims in print.\nThat whereas advertising can per\nsuade people to buy an automobile, only the\ncar itseH can keep tiiWn permanently sold.\nAnd that the endorsement of 750.000\nOverland owners means more than all we\ncan publish ourselves.\nThe Overland motor car is a good in\nvestment.\nIfc.Cdumb~ WILLYS OVERLAND, Inc. SsSsl*\nBronxi 2436 Grand Concourse fnear 18?th Street*. Tel. Fordhatn 5340.\nBrooklyn: Corner Fulton Street and Bedford Avenue. Tel. Bedford 8800.\nNewark: Rroad Street. Tel. Mulberry 4020.","height":"24207","width":"19224"}}
